quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  46,6,"Si yim…ďe …ďen moo…ďoyaama [ka Darngal], …ói ngontanoyat …ďe a√Ī…ďe, …ďe ngona e jeddugol ko …ďe ndewaynoo…ói kon."
  46,7,"Si aayeeje Amen …ďanngu…óe …óen janngaama e ma…ď…ďe, yedunoo…ďe goonga …ďen tuma nde arnoo e ma…ď…ďe …ďen mbi'a: "∆äuum ko mbilewu …ďanngu ngu"."
  46,8,"Kaa …ďe wi'at woni :"O pekindi nde?" Awa maaku: "Si taw mi pefkndi nde, awa doo on duncantaa lam hu'unde e [lepte] Allah …óen. Ko KaŇčko …ďuri anndude oon, tuma nde jumpoton e mayre. O yonii seedee hakkunde am e mon. Ko KaŇčko woni kaforowo, jurmotoo…óo On."
  46,9,"Maaku: "Mi wonaa adano e Nulaa…ďe …ďeen; mi anndaa kadi ko wa…óetee mi, maa ko wa…óete…óon. Mi jokkaa si wonaa ko wahayinaa kon e am; mi laataaki si wonaa jeertinoowo …ďanngina"."
  46,10,"Maaku: "Yeetee kam, si tawii le konde iwrunde ka Allah, njeddu…óon …óum, seedotoo…óo e …ďi…ó…ďe Israa'ila …ďen ceedii e [sellugol] …óum, o gooŇč…óini, onon kan towniti…óon...Pellet, Allah feewnata yim…ďe too√Īoo…ďe …ďeen."
  46,11,"Yeddu…ďe …ďen wi'ani gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďen: "Si tawno …óuum ko mo∆ī∆īere, …ďeen (waasu…ďe) adototaako men e mum". Nde wonunoo …ďe fewnoraani nde, ma …ďe mbi'u: "Ndee ko fenaande nee…ďunde!"."
  46,12,"Hino aditiinde, deftere Muusaa nden, …óowornde e yurmeende. Ndee …óoo kadi, ko deftere gooŇč…óinir- nde […óeya defte] e …óemngal aarabu, fii yo jeertinir (nde) too√Īoo…ďe …ďen e weltinirnde mo∆ī∆īinoo…ďe …ďeen."
  46,13,"Pellet, wi'u…ďe …ďeen: "Ko Allah woni Joomi amen", refti …ďe tabiti (e gooŇč…óinal), kulol alanaa …ďeen, wonaa kam…ďe cunoytoo."
  46,14,"Ko …ďeen ngoni yim…ďe Aljanna …ďeen duumotoo…ďe ton, njo…ďdi ko …ďe ngollatnoo kon."